# @rnbo/js
Run exported RNBO Patches in a web browser and integrate them into your applications.

## Installation

```sh
npm install @rnbo/js
```

## Documentation

See [https://rnbo.cycling74.com](https://rnbo.cycling74.com)

## API

See [https://rnbo.cycling74.com/js](https://rnbo.cycling74.com/js)
